{"word":"G4841 - συμπάσχω - sympáschō - soom-pas'-kho - Suffer with","slug":"G4841","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπάσχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sympáschō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-pas'-kho"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Suffer with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C7;&#x03C9; - sumpascho&#x0304;</b> - <i>soom-pas'-kho</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a> (including its alternate); to <i>experience pain jointly</i> or of the <i>same kind</i> (specifically <i>persecution</i>; to &ldquo;sympathize&rdquo;): - suffer with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}